02:13.998 --> 02:17.117
Everyone get up
and go in there, quick!

02:18.397 --> 02:20.117
Move, you too!

02:22.756 --> 02:24.954
Are you still here? Move!

02:24.956 --> 02:29.673
Get on your knees. You too.
On your knees. Let's go.

02:29.675 --> 02:32.353
