27:14.708 --> 27:19.184
- All right. Maybe I'll see you later.
- Maybe.

27:19.186 --> 27:22.506
Have a good night. Bye, Fabrizia.

27:28.905 --> 27:30.705
Everything okay, Patrizia?

27:42.663 --> 27:45.142
