27:47.542 --> 27:50.381
Sorry, can you make another one?
It's no good.

28:12.018 --> 28:13.777
Patrizia!

28:15.457 --> 28:17.216
Patrizia, stop!

28:41.332 --> 28:44.091
I'm Carmine,
he's my brother Santiago.

28:44.093 --> 28:45.650
Pleasure, Ilenia.

28:45.652 --> 28:47.572
- She's Anna.
- Pleasure.

28:51.331 --> 28:53.771
- Wanna dance?
- Let's dance.

29:04.129 --> 29:06.246
- Want some coke?
- No, I got no money.

29:06.249 --> 29:08.648
- It's a present.
- Wait.

29:10.048 --> 29:11.686
What happened?

29:11.688 --> 29:14.246
He wants to give us some coke,
what do we do?

29:14.248 --> 29:16.727
What do we do? We take it.

29:18.167 --> 29:19.926
Okay, let's go.

30:12.598 --> 30:15.237
- Turn it off.
- No, or else they'll hear us.

30:51.112 --> 30:54.229
- Santiago, got something to snort with?
- No, nothing.

30:54.231 --> 30:55.910
You got anything?

30:57.070 --> 31:00.270
- Turn off the water.
- Here.

32:10.418 --> 32:13.377
- Got any more?
- Wait here.

32:24.015 --> 32:26.053
What are you going to do?
We're outta cash.

32:26.055 --> 32:28.095
You'll see.

32:57.570 --> 32:59.410
- Give me 20.
- Another one?

33:00.570 --> 33:02.369
Another one.

33:07.529 --> 33:09.526
Bro', you got five?

33:09.528 --> 33:11.767
