37:13.407 --> 37:16.887
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

37:22.086 --> 37:25.445
- Welcome back, Donna Patrizia.
- Hi, Nicola.

37:53.640 --> 37:55.361
Leave us.

38:04.119 --> 38:06.236
Well?

38:06.238 --> 38:08.878
- Sorry, Donna Patrizia.
